Subject: Computers seems "Licensed" even after EPP automatically released license
Description:
Hello,

Customer name is Privat Bank.
They showed us a display bug when Computers in Device Control, seems "Licensed" even after EPP automatically released license.
The automatic release license function is set to 3 days, but computers which was last online more than 3 days, are displaying like "licensed", but we checked these computers in the "View license" menu, and they actually have no licenses.
So, it's only displaying issue.
I will attach screenshots.
